			<div class="gallerytext">The opening setup of <a href="/wiki/International_draughts" title="International draughts">international draughts</a>, which uses a 10×10 checkerboard</div>
		</li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 205px">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 200px;"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:CheckersStandard.jpg" class="mw-file-description" title="English draughts tournament standard"><img alt="English draughts tournament standard" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f1/CheckersStandard.jpg/250px-CheckersStandard.jpg" decoding="async" width="181" height="120" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f1/CheckersStandard.jpg/330px-CheckersStandard.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f1/CheckersStandard.jpg/500px-CheckersStandard.jpg 2x" data-file-width="3008" data-file-height="2000"></a></span></div>
