    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle \displaystyle {f(m,n)}={\begin{cases}{\text{black}}&amp;{\text{if}}\ m+n{\text{ is even}},\\{\text{white}}&amp;{\text{if}}\ m+n{\text{ is odd}}\\\end{cases}}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/ad1afbf6dfb96f7f9f25210b7858312c7e8f8309" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -2.505ex; width:37.198ex; height:6.176ex;" alt="{\displaystyle \displaystyle {f(m,n)}={\begin{cases}{\text{black}}&amp;{\text{if}}\ m+n{\text{ is even}},\\{\text{white}}&amp;{\text{if}}\ m+n{\text{ is odd}}\\\end{cases}}}"></span>
</p><p>The element <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle (m,n)=(0,0)}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>
        <mi>m</mi>
        <mo>,</mo>
        <mi>n</mi>
        <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>
        <mo>=</mo>
        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>
        <mn>0</mn>
        <mo>,</mo>
        <mn>0</mn>
        <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle (m,n)=(0,0)}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/d95398c6828c62a2bea0a54d47c41aa0d34781eb" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:14.545ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="{\displaystyle (m,n)=(0,0)}"></span> is black and represents the lower left corner of the board.
</p>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="Encoding">Encoding</h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Checkerboard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Encoding"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>In Unicode, checkerboard characters are encoded at various code points:
</p>
<ul><li><span class="nowrap"><style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r886049734">.mw-parser-output .monospaced{font-family:monospace,monospace}</style><span class="monospaced">U+2427</span> </span><span style="font-size:125%;line-height:1em">␧</span> <span style="font-variant: small-caps; text-transform: lowercase; font-feature-settings: 'onum'">SYMBOL FOR DELETE SQUARE CHECKER BOARD FORM</span></li>
<li><span class="nowrap"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886049734"><span class="monospaced">U+2428</span> </span><span style="font-size:125%;line-height:1em">␨</span> <span style="font-variant: small-caps; text-transform: lowercase; font-feature-settings: 'onum'">SYMBOL FOR DELETE RECTANGULAR CHECKER BOARD FORM</span></li>
<li><span class="nowrap"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886049734"><span class="monospaced">U+1F67E</span> </span><span style="font-size:125%;line-height:1em">🙾</span> <span style="font-variant: small-caps; text-transform: lowercase; font-feature-settings: 'onum'">CHECKER BOARD</span></li>
<li><span class="nowrap"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886049734"><span class="monospaced">U+1F67F</span> </span><span style="font-size:125%;line-height:1em">🙿</span> <span style="font-variant: small-caps; text-transform: lowercase; font-feature-settings: 'onum'">REVERSE CHECKER BOARD</span></li>
<li><span class="nowrap"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886049734"><span class="monospaced">U+1FB95</span> </span><span style="font-size:125%;line-height:1em">🮕</span> <span style="font-variant: small-caps; text-transform: lowercase; font-feature-settings: 'onum'">CHECKER BOARD FILL</span></li>
<li><span class="nowrap"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886049734"><span class="monospaced">U+1FB96</span> </span><span style="font-size:125%;line-height:1em">🮖</span> <span style="font-variant: small-caps; text-transform: lowercase; font-feature-settings: 'onum'">INVERSE CHECKER BOARD FILL</span></li></ul>
